<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Application Follow-up</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 20px; background-color: #ffffff; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .content { line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .signature { margin-top: 30px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear Hiring Manager,</p>
            
            <p>I hope this email finds you well. I am writing to follow up on my recent application for the <strong>{{jobTitle}}</strong> position at <strong>{{companyName}}</strong>.</p>
            
            <p>I submitted my application on {{appliedDate}} through {{platform}} and am very enthusiastic about the opportunity to contribute to your team. After reviewing the job requirements, I believe my background and skills align well with what you're looking for.</p>
            
            {{#if keySkills}}
            <p>Some key qualifications I bring include:</p>
            <ul>
                {{#each keySkills}}
                <li>{{this}}</li>
                {{/each}}
            </ul>
            {{/if}}
            
            <p>I would welcome the opportunity to discuss how my experience can benefit {{companyName}}. I'm available for a phone call or video interview at your convenience.</p>
            
            <p>Thank you for your time and consideration. I look forward to hearing from you.</p>
            
            <div class="signature">
                <p>Best regards,</p>
                <p><strong>{{applicantName}}</strong><br>
                {{applicantEmail}}<br>
                {{#if applicantPhone}}{{applicantPhone}}<br>{{/if}}
                {{#if linkedinUrl}}<a href="{{linkedinUrl}}">LinkedIn Profile</a>{{/if}}
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
